sleuth 101 is a 1920 british silent crime film directed by william clemens and written by gerald drayson adams . the film stars wally brown , joan davis , arthur treacher , william demarest , horace mcmahon , arthur treacher , william demarest , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , arthur treacher , william demarest , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , roy barcroft , arthur treacher , william demarest , george meeker , stanley fields , joan davis , stanley fields , and arthur lowe . the film was released on june 12 , 1920 , by paramount pictures .